    Recommendation\n                                                            
                                                                                
    Fix: Modify destroy_list to capture the next pointer before deleting the    
    current node (see the minimal fix above). For a long‑term, safer codebase,  
    encapsulate the linked‑list in a class that performs the same safe          
    traversal in its destructor and provides a clear() method.                  
                                                                                
